<h4 id="page-heading">Routes Home Page</h4>

<p>This page contains a list of all of your routes. This list contains
several different links. If you would like to view a route on the provided map,
select <img src="/img/icon/arrow.png" /> <span class="bold">Show in Place</span>. Selecting the <img
		src="/img/icon/route.png"
/> <span class="bold">Route Name</span> will take you to a specific route's detail page.</p>

<p>The column headings are active links that can be clicked to sort the list.
The routes list will update automatically once the sorting process is started.
Sorting can be completed on Date, Route Name, and Distance.</p>